item.title: Qt Release Madness
item.description: Qt 4.5 is out. Did you hear the loud sigh of relief coming all the way from the Troll offices? Now it’s time for cake. Development has been working hard on this release, it’s packed with new features and it’s the first version to be released under the LGPL. There was a lot of good feedback beforehand and we’re confident that this release is a good one. Or as Jason puts it on his blog on the labs:
